data: {"type":"layer1","modelId":"local/apple-fm","model":"Crucible (offline)","text":"```json\n{\n  \"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#\",\n  \"title\": \"IPv4 Address\",\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"address\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\",\n      \"pattern\": \"^((25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]{2}){3}$\",\n      \"description\": \"A valid IPv4 address\"\n    },\n    \"prefix\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\",\n      \"description\": \"Optional prefix length for CIDR notation\"\n    },\n    \"version\": {\n      \"type\": \"integer\",\n      \"minimum\": 4,\n      \"maximum\": 4,\n      \"description\": \"Version of the IPv4 address\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"required\": [\"address\", \"version\"]\n}\n```","done":true}

